test_data_2.term: a prominently displayed ancient temple painting and parked black bicycle
test_data_2.tag:
The image captures a vibrant street scene showcasing an art gallery or shop. The foreground features a black bicycle resting against a wall, its wheels slightly turned, suggesting it has just been parked. To the right, a large, colorful painting of an ancient temple, possibly Angkor Wat, is prominently displayed on an easel.

One monk gestures animatedly, perhaps pointing towards something of interest, while the other listens intently. Below them, an elderly man in an orange sweater and a woman in a yellow skirt stand on the steps, seemingly engaged in a discussion. The woman appears contemplative, while the man gestures with his hands, indicating a lively exchange.

The contrast between the innocence of the children and the adult world around them creates a poignant moment, inviting viewers to reflect on the simplicity of childhood amidst the complexities of city life.
